{"type":"message","id":"6638df5e","parentId":"82d7a66d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:58:22.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Paul Simulator masih up dan jalan:\n\n- **URL:** https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd ✅\n- **Guide:** https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd/guide.html ✅\n- **PM2:** online, uptime 35 jam, memory 97MB, no restarts\n- **Status:** healthy 👍\n\nTerakhir build-nya 31 Maret — PIN auth, character sheet, 3D dice, initiative tracker, spell book, NPC/monster generator, combat integration, Obsidian sync. Semua udah masuk.\n\nAda yang mau ditambahin atau di-fix buat Paul?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":173,"cacheRead":36776,"cacheWrite":151,"totalTokens":37101,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.004325,"cacheRead":0.018387999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00094375,"total":0.02366175}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775231896742}}
