{"type":"message","id":"da70045f","parentId":"00aafe91","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:03:40.809Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_JpwO5j26JpXhbZ8xeA8ydN","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-03.md","content":"# Memory — April 3, 2026\n\n## Lucy's Research Session\n\nLucy lagi browsing GitHub, riset tools/projects. Belum ada action item — pure exploration.\n\n### Repos yang di-review:\n\n1. **Hermes Agent** (NousResearch/hermes-agent)\n   - Open-source agent platform, competitor langsung OpenClaw\n   - Self-improving skill loop, Honcho user modeling, 6 terminal backends (incl. serverless Modal/Daytona)\n   - Punya `hermes claw migrate` — migration tool dari OpenClaw\n   - agentskills.io open standard\n   - Takeaway: skill auto-improvement loop & serverless backends worth watching\n\n2. **OpenClaude** (Gitlawb/openclaude)\n   - Claude Code fork, dibuat provider-agnostic (OpenAI, Gemini, DeepSeek, Ollama, Bedrock)\n   - Coding agent CLI only — no messaging, no memory, no multi-agent\n   - Agent routing per task (cheap model for simple, expensive for complex)\n   - Scope kecil dibanding OpenClaw/Hermes\n\n3. **OpenTrader** (Open-Trader/opentrader)\n   - Self-hosted crypto trading bot, npm install\n   - Grid, DCA, RSI strategies built-in + custom\n   - 100+ exchanges via CCXT (Binance, OKX, Bybit, dll)\n   - Paper trading + backtesting\n   - Bisa jalan di VPS kita (Node.js v22+)\n   - Lucy belum decide mau install atau nggak\n\n## Paul Simulator Status Check\n- Still running: https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd ✅\n- PM2: online, 35h uptime, 97MB memory, healthy\n- No changes requested\n"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":536,"cacheRead":40273,"cacheWrite":143,"totalTokens":40953,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0134,"cacheRead":0.020136499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00089375,"total":0.034