{"type":"message","id":"90d30a74","parentId":"56184dfa","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:06:59.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_yB8ALv11MI3OJPQ8kdfXUw","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  function renderClassDetail(c) {\n    const isID = _lang === 'id';\n\n    // Proficiencies section\n    let profHtml = `<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>${isID ? 'Profisiensi' : 'Proficiencies'}</h3>`;\n    if (c.profArmor?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Armor' : 'Armor'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profArmor.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profWeapons?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Senjata' : 'Weapons'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profWeapons.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profTools?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Alat' : 'Tools'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profTools.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profSaves?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profSaves.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profSkills?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Skill (pilih 2)' : 'Skills (choose 2)'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profSkills.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    profHtml += '</div>';\n\n    // Features by level\n    let featHtml = `<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>${isID ? 'Fitur per Level' : 'Features by Level'}</h3><div class=\"class-features-list\">`;\n    const features = c.features || [];\n    let currentLevel = -1;\n    features.forEach(f => {\n      if (f.level !== currentLevel) {\n        currentLevel = f.level;\n      }\n      featHtml += `\n        <div class=\"class-feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"feature-header\">\n            <span class=\"feature-name\">${escapeHtml(f.name)}</span>\n            <span class=\"feature-level\">Lvl ${f.level}</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature-body\">${formatDesc(f.entries)}</div>\n        </div>`;\n    });\n    featHtml += '</div></div>';\n\n    // Subclasses\n    let scHtml = '';\n    if (c.subclasses && c.subclasses.length > 0) {\n      scHtml = `<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>${isID ? 'Subkelas' : 'Subclasses'} (${c.subclasses.length})</h3>`;\n      c.subclasses.forEach(sc => {\n        const scFeats = (sc.features || []);\n        scHtml += `\n          <div class=\"subclass-group\">\n            <div class=\"subclass-group-header\">\n              <span>${escapeHtml(sc.name)}</span>\n              <span style=\"font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-dim)\">${scFeats.length} ${isID ? 'fitur' : 'features'} ▾</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"subclass-group-body\">\n              <div class=\"class-features-list\">`;\n        scFeats.forEach(f => {\n          scHtml += `\n                <div class=\"class-feature-item\">\n                  <div class=\"feature-header\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-name\">${escapeHtml(f.name)}</span>\n                    <span class=\"feature-level\">Lvl ${f.level}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"feature-body\">${formatDesc(f.entries)}</div>\n                </div>`;\n        });\n        scHtml += '</div></div></div>';\n      });\n      scHtml += '</div>';\n    }\n\n    return `\n      <div class=\"comp-detail-title\">${escapeHtml(c.name)}</div>\n      <div class=\"comp-detail-subtitle\">${isID ? 'Hit Dice' : 'Hit Dice'}: ${c.hitDice || '?'} · Saving Throws: ${(c.profSaves || []).join(', ')}${c.spellcastingAbility ? ` · ${isID ? 'Sihir' : 'Spellcasting'}: ${c.spellcastingAbility}` : ''}</div>\n      ${profHtml}\n      ${featHtml}\n      ${scHtml}\n    `;\n  }\n\n  function renderRaceDetail(r) {\n    const isID = _lang === 'id';\n    return `\n      <div class=\"comp-detail-title\">${escapeHtml(r.name)}</div>\n      <div class=\"comp-detail-subtitle\">${isID ? 'Kecepatan' : 'Speed'}: ${r.speed || 30} ft · ${isID ? 'Ukuran' : 'Size'}: ${r.size || 'Medium'}${r.darkvision ? ` · Darkvision ${r.darkvision} ft.` : ''}</div>\n      ${r.abilityBonuses?.length ? `<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>${isID ? 'Skor Kemampuan' : 'Ability Scores'}</h3><p>${escapeHtml(r.abilityBonuses.join(', '))}</p></div>` : ''}\n      <div class=\"comp-detail-section\">\n        <h3>${isID ? 'Sifat' : 'Traits'}</h3>\n        <div class=\"comp-desc-text\"><p>${formatDesc(r.entries)}</p></div>\n      </div>\n      ${r.traitTags?.length ? `<div class=\"comp-detail-tags\">${r.traitTags.map(t => `<span class=\"comp-detail-tag\">${escapeHtml(t)}</span>`).join('')}</div>` : ''}\n\n[161 more lines in file. Use offset=9342 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232419271}}
{"type":"message","id":"a45e712f","parentId":"90d30a74","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:07.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I can see — the feature descriptions (`f.entries`) come from the SRD JSON and they're all in English. The translation system only covers descriptions for specific categories (spells, monsters, classes summary, species, etc.) but NOT the detailed class features (Rage, Reckless Attack, etc.).\n\nLet me check what the classes data looks like:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_zpg6Y3GcrA4oXqSRKMSylR","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/5etools/all-classes.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\nif isinstance(data, list):\n    barb = [c for c in data if c.get('name','').lower() == 'barbarian']\n    if barb:\n        features = barb[0].get('features', [])[:3]\n        for f in features:\n            print(json.dumps(f, indent=2)[:400])\n            print('---')\nelif isinstance(data, dict):\n    print(list(data.keys())[:5])\n\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"Trying other structure...\""}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":303,"cacheRead":68068,"cacheWrite":1684,"totalTokens":70056,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.007575,"cacheRead":0.034034,"cacheWrite":0.010525000000000001,"total":0.052139}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232419290}}
{"type":"message","id":"730320c3","parentId":"a45e712f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:07.445Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_zpg6Y3GcrA4oXqSRKMSylR","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"Rage\",\n  \"level\": 1,\n  \"entries\": \"You can imbue yourself with a primal power called Rage, a force that grants you extraordinary might and resilience. You can enter it as a Bonus Action if you aren't wearing Heavy armor.\\n\\nYou can enter your Rage the number of times shown for your Barbarian level in the Rages column of the Barbarian Features table. You regain one expended use when yo\n---\n{\n  \"name\": \"Unarmored Defense\",\n  \"level\": 1,\n  \"entries\": \"While you aren't wearing any armor, your base Armor Class equals 10 plus your Dexterity and Constitution modifiers. You can use a Shield and still gain this benefit.\"\n}\n---\n{\n  \"name\": \"Weapon Mastery\",\n  \"level\": 1,\n  \"entries\": \"Your training with weapons allows you to use the weapon mastery properties of two kinds of Simple or Martial Melee weapons of your choice, such as Greataxe and Handaxe. Whenever you finish a Long Rest, you can practice weapon drills and change one of those weapon choices.\\n\\nWhen you reach certain Barbarian levels, you gain the ability to u\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":75,"aggregated":"{\n  \"name\": \"Rage\",\n  \"level\": 1,\n  \"entries\": \"You can imbue yourself with a primal power called Rage, a force that grants you extraordinary might and resilience. You can enter it as a Bonus Action if you aren't wearing Heavy armor.\\n\\nYou can enter your Rage the number of times shown for your Barbarian level in the Rages column of the Barbarian Features table. You regain one expended use when yo\n---\n{\n  \"name\": \"Unarmored Defense\",\n  \"level\": 1,\n  \"entries\": \"While you aren't wearing any armor, your base Armor Class equals 10 plus your Dexterity and Constitution modifiers. You can use a Shield and still gain this benefit.\"\n}\n---\n{\n  \"name\": \"Weapon Mastery\",\n  \"level\": 1,\n  \"entries\": \"Your training with weapons allows you to use the weapon mastery properties of two kinds of Simple or Martial Melee weapons of your choice, such as Greataxe and Handaxe. Whenever you finish a Long Rest, you can practice weapon drills and change one of those weapon choices.\\n\\nWhen you reach certain Barbarian levels, you gain the ability to u\n---","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232427433}}
{"type":"message","id":"79ad0268","parentId":"730320c3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:14.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found it. The class features are in `all-classes.json`. These need translation. This is a big job — let me count how many features there are:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_OdYdlflUFk9TPs2SloR3mT","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/5etools/all-classes.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\ntotal = 0\nfor c in data:\n    features = c.get('features', [])\n    subclasses = c.get('subclasses', [])\n    sc_features = sum(len(sc.get('features', [])) for sc in subclasses)\n    print(f\\\"{c['name']}: {len(features)} features, {len(subclasses)} subclasses ({sc_features} sc features)\\\")\n    total += len(features) + sc_features\nprint(f'\\\\nTotal: {total} features to translate')\n\""}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":265,"cacheRead":69752,"cacheWrite":611,"totalTokens":70629,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.006625000000000001,"cacheRead":0.034876,"cacheWrite":0.00381875,"total":0.045324750000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232427451}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bc57901","parentId":"79ad0268","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:14.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_OdYdlflUFk9TPs2SloR3mT","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Barbarian: 26 features, 4 subclasses (22 sc features)\nBard: 18 features, 4 subclasses (24 sc features)\nCleric: 22 features, 4 subclasses (24 sc features)\nDruid: 23 features, 4 subclasses (27 sc features)\nFighter: 27 features, 4 subclasses (33 sc features)\nMonk: 34 features, 4 subclasses (26 sc features)\nPaladin: 24 features, 4 subclasses (25 sc features)\nRanger: 23 features, 4 subclasses (25 sc features)\nRogue: 32 features, 4 subclasses (28 sc features)\nSorcerer: 19 features, 4 subclasses (25 sc features)\nWarlock: 19 features, 4 subclasses (26 sc features)\nWizard: 16 features, 4 subclasses (24 sc features)\n\nTotal: 592 features to translate"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":76,"aggregated":"Barbarian: 26 features, 4 subclasses (22 sc features)\nBard: 18 features, 4 subclasses (24 sc features)\nCleric: 22 features, 4 subclasses (24 sc features)\nDruid: 23 features, 4 subclasses (27 sc features)\nFighter: 27 features, 4 subclasses (33 sc features)\nMonk: 34 features, 4 subclasses (26 sc features)\nPaladin: 24 features, 4 subclasses (25 sc features)\nRanger: 23 features, 4 subclasses (25 sc features)\nRogue: 32 features, 4 subclasses (28 sc features)\nSorcerer: 19 features, 4 subclasses (25 sc features)\nWarlock: 19 features, 4 subclasses (26 sc features)\nWizard: 16 features, 4 subclasses (24 sc features)\n\nTotal: 592 features to translate","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232434108}}
{"type":"message","id":"3624bec0","parentId":"1bc57901","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:20.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"592 fitur. Ini banyak banget — mau gw approach begini:\n\n1. Gw translate semua 592 feature descriptions ke Bahasa Indonesia\n2. Simpan di translation file\n3. Update render code supaya pakai translation kalau bahasa = ID\n\nTapi ini bakal makan waktu & token lumayan karena 592 paragraf. Mau gw mulai sekarang? Atau prioritasin class tertentu dulu (misal Barbarian dulu buat Paul)?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":126,"cacheRead":70363,"cacheWrite":545,"totalTokens":71035,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00315,"cacheRead":0.0351815,"cacheWrite":0.00340625,"total":0.041742749999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232434128}}
{"type":"message","id":"c839fd2c","parentId":"3624bec0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:23.008Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"AC2F3D30124F55305786509E819474F7\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"3EB0A67A4D72A7BA18C03D\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"246248208642099@lid\",\n  \"body\": \"Ini buat Paul Simulator ya? Gw translate semua text Rage yang keliatan di screenshot:\\n\\n---\\n\\n*Rage (Amukan)* — Lvl 1\\n\\nKamu bisa meresapi dirimu dengan kekuatan primal yang disebut Rage (Amukan), sebuah kekuatan yang memberimu tenaga dan ketahanan luar biasa. Kamu bisa mengaktifkannya sebagai Bonus Action selama kamu tidak memakai Heavy Armor (Baju Besi Berat).\\n\\nKamu bisa mengaktifkan Rage sebanyak jumlah yang tertera di kolom \\\"Rages\\\" pada tabel Barbarian Features sesuai level Barbarian-mu. Kamu mendapatkan kembali satu penggunaan yang sudah terpakai saat menyelesaikan Short Rest, dan mendapatkan kembali semua penggunaan saat menyelesaikan Long Rest.\\n\\nSelama aktif, Rage mengikuti aturan di bawah ini.\\n\\n*Damage Resistance (Ketahanan Damage)*\\n\\nKamu memiliki Resistance terhadap damage Bludgeoning (Pukul), Piercing (Tusuk), dan Slashing (Tebas).\\n\\n*Rage Damage (Damage Amukan)*\\n\\nSaat kamu melakukan serangan menggunakan Strength — baik dengan senjata maupun Unarmed Strike (Serangan Tangan Kosong) — dan mengenai target, kamu mendapat bonus damage yang meningkat seiring level.\\n\\n---\\n\\nIni cuma yang keliatan di screenshot. Mau gw translate semua fitur Barbarian sekaligus (Reckless Attack, Danger Sense, dll) biar langsung lengkap? Atau ada class/feature lain yang perlu di-translate juga buat Paul?\"\n}\n```\n\nbukan , aku suka cara penerjemahan mu, nah semua yang ada di kompedium, isinya TERJEMAHKAN SEMUA , untuk versi bahasa indo, soalnya banyak yg g paham b inggris"}],"timestamp":1775232442963}}
{"type":"message","id":"cffb068c","parentId":"c839fd2c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:30.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, clear — translate SEMUA isi Compendium ke Bahasa Indonesia. 592 class features + subclass features. Gw mulai sekarang, dispatch ke sub-agent biar parallel dan cepat."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_5sAnRChI6s6WP090ZOXQM0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/5etools/all-classes.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\n\n# Extract ALL features with their entries\nfor c in data:\n    print(f'=== {c[\\\"name\\\"]} ===')\n    for f in c.get('features', []):\n        entry = f.get('entries','')\n        print(f'  [{f[\\\"level\\\"]}] {f[\\\"name\\\"]}: {entry[:80]}...')\n\" 2>/dev/null | head -80"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":253,"cacheRead":26557,"cacheWrite":44416,"totalTokens":71229,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.006325,"cacheRead":0.013278499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.2776,"total":0.2972185}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232442993}}
