{"type":"message","id":"a3a9daed","parentId":"7ab19c27","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:07:48.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a massive translation job. Let me spawn a sub-agent to handle this efficiently — it'll translate all features in batches and write them to the translation file."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_a6ecaxeTaINtfZ0tglNA7S","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are translating D&D 2024 PHB class features from English to Bahasa Indonesia for a web app compendium. \n\nThe translation style should be:\n- Game mechanical terms kept in English (Hit Points, Armor Class, Saving Throw, Advantage, Disadvantage, Bonus Action, etc.)\n- Flavor/description text translated to natural Indonesian\n- Feature names: keep English name + Indonesian translation in parentheses where helpful\n- Example style: \"Kamu bisa meresapi dirimu dengan kekuatan primal yang disebut Rage, sebuah kekuatan yang memberimu tenaga dan ketahanan luar biasa.\"\n\nTASK:\n1. Read /home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/5etools/all-classes.json to get ALL class features and subclass features\n2. Read /home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/srd/translations-id.json to understand the existing translation structure\n3. Create a new section in the translations file called \"class_features\" that maps \"className.featureName\" -> translated description\n4. Also create \"subclass_features\" section mapping \"subclassName.featureName\" -> translated description\n5. Translate ALL 592 features (12 classes + all subclasses)\n\nWrite the updated translations-id.json when done.\n\nAfter updating translations, modify /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js:\n- In the renderClassDetail function (around line 9262), make the feature body use translated text when lang=id\n- Add a helper function that looks up class_features[\"className.featureName\"] from _translations\n- Same for subclass features in the subclass rendering section\n\nThe lookup should work like:\n```\nfunction tClassFeature(className, featureName) {\n  if (_lang === 'en' || !_translations) return null;\n  const key = className.toLowerCase() + '.' + featureName.toLowerCase().replace(/\\s+/g, '-');\n  return _translations.class_features?.[key] || null;\n}\n```\n\nThen in renderClassDetail, replace:\n```\n<div class=\"feature-body\">${formatDesc(f.entries)}</div>\n```\nwith:\n```\n<div class=\"feature-body\">${formatDesc(tClassFeature(c.name, f.name) || f.entries)}</div>\n```\n\nSame pattern for subclass features.\n\nDo ALL 12 classes and ALL subclasses. No shortcuts. Every feature must be translated.","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":600}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":712,"cacheRead":70973,"cacheWrite":2406,"totalTokens":74092,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0178,"cacheRead":0.0354865,"cacheWrite":0.0150375,"total":0.068329}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232450374}}
