{"type":"message","id":"486b0f51","parentId":"997313b1","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:47:58.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is the key format — the JS function uses `name.toLowerCase().replace(/\\s+/g, '-')` but the subclass names in the JSON have spaces (like \"Path of the Berserker\") which should become \"path-of-the-berserker\", not \"path of the berserker\". Let me check:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_flkJhTa9KNghdnzvmr15i7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/5etools/all-classes.json') as f:\n    classes = json.load(f)\nfor c in classes[:2]:\n    for sc in c.get('subclasses', []):\n        print(f'Subclass name: \\\"{sc[\\\"name\\\"]}\\\"')\n\""}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":220,"cacheRead":143464,"cacheWrite":611,"totalTokens":144296,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0055000000000000005,"cacheRead":0.07173199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00381875,"total":0.08105574999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775234873079}}
{"type":"message","id":"052effd0","parentId":"486b0f51","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:47:58.761Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_flkJhTa9KNghdnzvmr15i7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Subclass name: \"Path of the Berserker\"\nSubclass name: \"Path of the Wild Heart\"\nSubclass name: \"Path of the World Tree\"\nSubclass name: \"Path of the Zealot\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Dance\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Glamour\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Lore\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Valor\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":82,"aggregated":"Subclass name: \"Path of the Berserker\"\nSubclass name: \"Path of the Wild Heart\"\nSubclass name: \"Path of the World Tree\"\nSubclass name: \"Path of the Zealot\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Dance\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Glamour\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Lore\"\nSubclass name: \"College of Valor\"","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775234878741}}
{"type":"message","id":"353eeb59","parentId":"052effd0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:48:09.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The JS function does `name.toLowerCase().replace(/\\s+/g, '-')` which turns \"Path of the Berserker\" into \"path-of-the-berserker\" — exactly matching our translation keys. But my Python test was wrong — it wasn't replacing spaces with hyphens. The JS code is correct. Let me verify properly:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_JpSZNGYmaqZ2BmZKMCVCMC","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport re, json\n\ndef js_key(name, feat):\n    return re.sub(r'\\s+', '-', name.lower()) + '.' + re.sub(r'\\s+', '-', feat.lower()).replace(\\\"'\\\", '')\n\nwith open('/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/5etools/all-classes.json') as f:\n    classes = json.load(f)\nwith open('/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/srd/translations-id.json') as f:\n    t = json.load(f)\n\ncf = t['class_features']\nsf = t['subclass_features']\n\nmissing_cf = 0\ntotal_cf = 0\nfor c in classes:\n    for f in c.get('features', []):\n        key = js_key(c['name'], f['name'])\n        total_cf += 1\n        if key not in cf:\n            missing_cf += 1\n            if missing_cf <= 3:\n                print(f'Missing class: {key}')\n\nmissing_sf = 0\ntotal_sf = 0\nfor c in classes:\n    for sc in c.get('subclasses', []):\n        for f in sc.get('features', []):\n            key = js_key(sc['name'], f['name'])\n            total_sf += 1\n            if key not in sf:\n                missing_sf += 1\n                if missing_sf <= 5:\n                    print(f'Missing subclass: {key}')\n\nprint(f'\\\\nClass features: {total_cf - missing_cf}/{total_cf} translated ({missing_cf} missing)')\nprint(f'Subclass features: {total_sf - missing_sf}/{total_sf} translated ({missing_sf} missing)')\n\""}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":562,"cacheRead":144075,"cac