{"type":"message","id":"cdeea596","parentId":"48ceb015","timestamp":"2026-04-04T02:38:24.164Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/9b9c7635-74b7-4056-aa60-f8b1e10e2214.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-04 02:19:26 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ACBDD24FD8CA701585D16D45A385E298\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nhmm, gemma4, interesting"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1775270304091}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8240b3e","parentId":"cdeea596","timestamp":"2026-04-04T02:38:40.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGemma 4 dari Google, baru keluar kemarin di Ollama. 16 varian sekaligus — itu agresif.\n\nYang menarik dari lineup-nya:\n\n**Yang worth noting:**\n- **gemma4:e2b** — 7.2GB, 128K context. Ini kecil banget tapi multimodal (Text + Image). Bisa jalan di HP atau VPS kita.\n- **gemma4:e4b** — 9.6GB, yang jadi `latest`. Sweet spot antara size dan capability.\n- **gemma4:26b** — 18GB, 256K context. Ini yang serius — context window gede, dan 26B parameter udah bisa nalar lumayan.\n- **gemma4:31b** — 20GB, 256K context. Top tier dari lineup ini.\n\n**Kenapa interesting:**\n- 256K context di model 26B/31B yang bisa jalan lokal — itu lebih gede dari Claude Sonnet (200K)\n- Semua support Image input — bisa OCR, bisa baca screenshot, bisa analisis dokumen\n- E2b (7.2GB) bisa jalan di VPS kita tanpa GPU, pake CPU aja meskipun lambat\n\n**Buat kita?** Kalau mau hemat Bedrock cost, gemma4:e4b atau e2b bisa jadi fallback model buat task-task ringan (summarize, translate, simple Q&A). Yang berat tetap Bedrock.\n\nLagi mau coba jalanin di Ollama, atau masih riset-riset aja?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":411,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":182586,"totalTokens":183000,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.010275000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":1.1411625,"total":1.1514525}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775270304146}}
